Package org.rapidcontext.util

Interface HttpUtil.METHOD

Enclosing interface:
HttpUtil
public static interface HttpUtil.METHOD
The HTTP methods as defined in RFC1945 (HTTP/1.0), RFC2616 (HTTP/1.1) and RFC5789 (PATCH).
